 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"nu Thai Lan\" title=\"n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/thai-lan-lan-thu-hai-lien-tiep-gianh-ve-tham-du-world-cup-bong-da-nu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan (xanh) \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Philippines \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2019</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eef Jordan \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2. V\u00e0 t\u1edbi t\u1ed1i qua 12/4, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, \u0110T n\u1eef Philippines. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i qua, Philippines \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;ch\u01a1i canh b\u1ea1c t\u1ea5t tay&rdquo;, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0103n c\u1ea3 ng\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan. Tuy nhi\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh v\u00ec Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n Philippines. V\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n Philippines &ldquo;l\u1eadt&rdquo; Th\u00e1i Lan th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai n\u00e0y, n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A sau \u0110T n\u1eef Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u00f4ng d\u00e2n nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh n\u00e0y gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2019 t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n Philippines x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng ba b\u1ea3ng A ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng ba b\u1ea3ng B sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1i nay \u0111\u1ec3 tranh su\u1ea5t th\u1ee9 n\u0103m ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111i Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 20h45 t\u1ed1i nay, hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t di\u1ec5n ra. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n g\u1eb7p \u00dac c\u00f2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 sang n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-nhac-toi-ong-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-han-quoc-168-184138.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-nhac-toi-ong-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-nhac-toi-ong-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-han-quoc-168-184138.html\">HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1e