ne;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua 1-4 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ai cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sai l\u1ea7m. \u1ede th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng CSKA Moscow \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil phat bieu ve tran CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal hinh anh\" title=\"Mesut Ozil ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Mesut-Ozil-phat-bieu-ve-tran-CSKA-Moscow-vs-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u1ed3n \u00e9p Arsenal. Ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 11 ph\u00fat, t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 39 \u0111\u1ebfn 50, CSKA Moscow ghi li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Fedor Chalov v\u00e0 Kirill Nababkin \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa h\u1ecd s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c Arsenal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1eabn mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e8 l\u00ean vai th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Welbeck \u1edf ph\u00fat 75 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch th\u1edf ph\u00e0o, sau \u0111\u00f3 Ramsey ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-3 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mesut Ozil th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ozil chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn CSKA Moscow 2-2 Arsenal, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil phat bieu ve tran Arsenal\" title=\"Mesut Ozil ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/vao-ban-ket-europa-league-mesut-ozil-thach-thuc-moi-doi-thu.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mesut Ozil ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn CSKA Moscow vs Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat lo l\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi Arsenal v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/koscielny-minh-oan-cho-wenger-sau-tran-hoa-cska-moscow-184-184134.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Koscielny c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</strong></span>, sau \u0111\u00f3 HLV Wenger c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. \u1ede b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 Atletico Madrid, Salzburg v\u00e0 Marseille.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/16176-40942/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1129","checkdouble":"184143"},{"date":"10:28 13/04","title":"Wenger ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Atletico \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/Mesut-Ozil-phat-bieu-ve-tran-CSKA-Moscow-vs-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;borde