 margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 H\u00f9m x\u00e1m m\u1eddi l\u1ea1i sau khi sa th\u1ea3i Carlo Ancelotti, HLV Jupp Heynckes s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n HLV ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, <strong>ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 HLV Niko Kovac</strong>, hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a CLB Eintracht Frankfurt. \u00d4ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean r\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Kicker chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam, Niko Kovac s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Allianz Arena trao cho b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 2 n\u0103m. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ngay khi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac, v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng th\u00e1ng B\u1ea3y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Niko Kovac s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Bayern Munich \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" title=\"Niko Kovac s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Bayern Munich \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/kovac.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Niko Kovac s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Bayern Munich \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m Eintracht Frankfurt t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3/2016 khi CLB l\u00f3p ng\u00f3p \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, Niko Kovac gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn playoff. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n, Frankfurt m\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh g\u1eaft gao v\u1edbi Bayer Leverkusen cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1ef1 Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Kovac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho Bayern Munich. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho H\u00f9m x\u00e1m, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Kovac t\u1eebng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Eintracht Frankfurt, nh\u01b0ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra: &ldquo;T\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd CLB n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng <strong>trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i</strong>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n 2 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, sau khi h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea7n ch\u1eeb v\u1edbi HLV Thomas Tuchel (nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gia nh\u1eadp PSG). M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c bao g\u1ed3m Ralf Hassenhuttl (Leipzig), Julian Nagelsmann (Hoffenheim) v\u00e0 Christian Streich c\u1ee7a Freiburg c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh t\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng Niko Kovac l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Niko Kovac \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 2 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Bayern t\u1eeb 2001-2003. \u00d4ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009 v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd. Ngo\u00e0i ra, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Bayern Munich c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Hasan Salihamidzic &ndash; G\u0110TT hi\u1ec7n nay c\u1ee7a H\u00f9m x\u00e1m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/vao-ban-ket-champions-league-hlv-bayern-noi-gi-184-184067.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/vao-ban-ket-champions-league-hlv-bayern-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/vao-ban-ket-champions-league-hlv-bayern-noi-gi-184-184067.html\">V\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, HLV Bayern n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nJupp Heynckes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Sevilla, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-tran-hoa-00-cua-bayern-truoc-sevilla-184-184063.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/thay-gi-sau-tran-hoa-00-cua-bayern-truoc-sevilla.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-tran-hoa-00-cua-bayern-truoc-sevilla-184-184063.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 c\u1ee7a Bayern tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla?</span><br>\r\nH\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Bayern v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1127","checkdouble":"184145"},{"date":"11:03 13/04","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/31/nguoi-dai-dien-chinh-thuc-chot-tuong-lai-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6