x; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar l\u00e0 cha c\u1ee7a anh, nh\u01b0ng si\u00eau c\u00f2 Pini Zahavi m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m trung gian trong v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Barca &ndash; PSG \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Pini Zahavi t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ee9ng sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Roman Abramovich mua Chelsea, v\u00e0 Man United chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rio Ferdinand. Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, si\u00eau c\u00f2 74 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Brazil v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;\u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1&rdquo; Neymar, nh\u1eb1m k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0y v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 ti\u1ebfp theo. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chia tay PSG.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zahavi cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Neymar \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi &ndash; Messi, Ronaldo, Neymar, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t CLB. T\u1ea1i Barca, Neymar lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 2. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, th\u1ee9 2 trong quy\u1ec1n \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 2 trong m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Real Madrid nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n\" title=\"Kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng Neymar gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, n\u1ebfu v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Ronaldo hay Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/nguoi-dai-dien-chinh-thuc-chot-tuong-lai-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Real Madrid nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 8-9 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec9nh cao ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Neymar c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 do, v\u00e0 PSG l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi theo d\u00f5i Ligue 1. Ch\u00ednh Neymar \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong kho\u1ea3ng 1-2 th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua, tin \u0111\u1ed3n Neymar r\u1eddi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u00f2n &ldquo;\u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc&rdquo; m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng, th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00fac l\u1ee3i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Neymar \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u1edf Ligue 1. Anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn \u1edf b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua cu\u1ed9c ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c, g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tin t\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 Neymar d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-neymar-cong-khai-hon-ban-gai-trong-rap-hat-188-183723.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Neymar c\u00f4ng khai h\u00f4n b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i trong r\u1ea1p h\u00e1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/neymar-giong-messi-hon-la-ronaldo-184-183686.html\">Neymar gi\u1ed1ng Messi h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/mbappe-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-neymar-toi-real-madrid-197-183323.html\">Mbappe n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/neymar-hay-day-nhung-khong-the-sanh-voi-cau-thu-50-nam-co-mot-184-183236.html\">&ldquo;Neymar hay \u0111\u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 50 n\u0103m c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/neymar-va-psg-khi-chung-ta-khong-thuoc-ve-nhau-184-181902.html\">Neymar v\u00e0 PSG: Khi ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nhau</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1126","checkdouble":"184146"},{"date":"10:59 13/04","title":"CSKA 2-2 Arsenal: Khi Arsene Wenger ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/cska-22-arsenal-khi-arsene-wenger-nghi-qua-nhieu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{borde