isplay:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thierry Henry ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1edbn m\u00e0y, hay c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng k\u00ecm n\u00e9n m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eeda mi\u1ec7ng. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec Arsenal \u0111ang l\u00e2m nguy, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ba b\u00e0n b\u1ecb san b\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c trong m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n l\u1ec5 \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng. Anh bi\u1ebft Arsene Wenger v\u1eeba m\u1edbi ph\u00e1 l\u1ec7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"44px\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding:10px;\" valign=\"top\"><em>Arsene m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ecbnh ra t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o chi ti\u1ebft cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i &ndash; &lsquo;\u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 n\u00e0y, canh ch\u1eebng h\u1eafn ta&hellip;&rsquo; &ndash; v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi duy nh\u1ea5t \u00f4ng \u1ea5y tr\u00f4ng mong t\u1eeb ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.</em><br>\r\n            <span style=\"color: #8bc53f; float: right;\"><em>Henry n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u0169, th\u00e1ng 12/2016.</em></span></td>\r\n            <td width=\"44px\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em><strong>&ldquo;Arsene kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd th\u00edch thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt hay s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh gi\u1eefa tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb quanh ph\u00fat 70 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;</strong></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ecf qua m\u1eb7t ng\u1eef ngh\u0129a, hai s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League 2017/18 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat 69 v\u00e0 77, nh\u01b0ng Wenger v\u1eabn su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa cho tan t\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi c\u00e1i ph\u00e1 l\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ec9a mai thay khi Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea5y Barcelona (c\u0169ng th\u1eafng 4-1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Roma 0-3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch) l\u00e0m b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i \u0111i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. T\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3... d\u00f9 c\u00f3 Wenger, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd c\u00f3 Wenger.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA 2-2 Arsenal Khi Arsene Wenger nghi qua nhieu hinh anh\" title=\"CSKA 2-2 Arsenal Khi Arsene Wenger ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Mesut-Ozil-phat-bieu-ve-tran-CSKA-Moscow-vs-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Suy ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7, Wenger su\u00fdt khi\u1ebfn Arsenal ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Wenger \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u1ed3n m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m t\u1eeb c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean do cho c\u01a1n ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ed1n di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ch\u1eadm r\u00e3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f2n Arsenal v\u1eabn gi\u1eef v\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 4-2 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 CSKA khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u0169ng cho Arsenal c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1eeda sai, x\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 n\u00ean l\u00e0 h\u1ed3i chu\u00f4ng c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh, nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u01b0 Roma v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ee9ng minh, hay ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng Marseille hay Salzburg ngay trong \u0111\u00eam \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Arsenal v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra, Wenger \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u cao h\u01a1n \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 - t\u1eadp trung h\u01a1n, m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch h\u01a1n, \u00fd ch\u00ed h\u01a1n, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n&hellip;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tran hoa cua Arsenal cho thay su nguy hiem cua nhung doi bong buoc phai don len chien dau.\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed3n l\u00ean chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/tu-tran-hoa-cua-arsenal-dung-dua-voi-nhung-ke-cung-duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>CSKA Moscow t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Wenger v\u00e0 su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 x\u1edbi tung m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n cho th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal c\u00e0ng h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Mohamed Elneny b\u1ecb k\u00e9o t\u1eeb trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 k\u00e9o theo, Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 m\u1ea5t d\u1ea1ng, c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. V\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n hai ph\u00fat sau, Kirill Nababkin nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch gi\u1edd m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tim \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n run \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y m\u1ecfng tang.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t Wenger b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng &ldquo;th\u00edch thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt hay s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh gi\u1eefa tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo; su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn Arsenal tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Sau 8 ph\u00fat quay cu\u1ed3ng b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, Elneny \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi t\u1ea1m b\u00ecnh \u1ed5n h\u01a1n. Ch\u00ednh tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap CLB th\u00e0nh London tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m r\u1eddi Moskva.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA 2-2 Arsenal Khi Arsene Wenger nghi qua nhieu hinh anh 3\" title=\"CSKA 2-2 Arsenal Khi Arsene Wenger ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/CSKA-2-2-Arsenal-Khi-Arsene-Wenger-nghi-qua-nhieu-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Wenger, ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a CSKA 2-2 Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ee3t nh\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 b\u1eadt b\u00e3i nh\u00e3n ti\u1ec1n ra \u0111\u1ea5y, Arsenal tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh trong 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. Danny Welbeck c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trong khi Aaron Ramsey ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh b\u1ebf t\u1eafc chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Arsenal ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i chu\u1ed7i 4 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1eb1ng m\u1ea1ch 7 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf v\u00ec sao m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u00f4ng vua ch\u1eb7ng n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00eam h\u00fat ch\u1ebft h\u00f4m nay m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ra \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 truy\u1ec1n l\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, tinh th\u1ea7n cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn ra m\u1ed9t Wenger b\u1ea3o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4i khi c\u0169ng suy ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn CSKA 2-2 Arsenal:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088893/013100\">CSKA 2-2 Arsenal</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tu-tran-hoa-cua-arsenal-dung-dua-voi-nhung-ke-cung-duong-184-184129.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/tu-tran-hoa-cua-arsenal-dung-dua-voi-nhung-ke-cung-duong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tu-tran-hoa-cua-arsenal-dung-dua-voi-nhung-ke-cung-duong-184-184129.html\">T\u1eeb tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Arsenal: \u0110\u1eebng \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng!</span><br>\r\nArsenal su\u00fdt n\u1eefa tr\u1ea3i qua b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga r\u1eb1ng bi k\u1ecbch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o th\u1ebf ch\u00e2n t\u01b0\u1eddng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1125","checkdouble":"184150"},{"date":"11:22 13/04","title":"Benzema c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/psg-mua-tien-dao-karim-benzema.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont