ecfi Real</strong></span>. T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 32 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, qu\u00e1 \u00edt so v\u1edbi trung phong c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG mua tien dao Karim Benzema cua Real hinh anh\" title=\"PSG mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/psg-mua-tien-dao-karim-benzema.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Benzema c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, Benzema r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 Bale c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cv\u1eadt t\u1ebf th\u1ea7n\u201d. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t d\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n h\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nPSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Benzema</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa hai ng\u00f4i sao Neymar v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a t\u1edbi nay. V\u00e0 khi ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i PSG mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Neymar nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Cavani c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u201c\u0111\u1ea5t s\u1ed1ng\u201d t\u1ea1i Real. Nghe \u0111\u00e2u Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG mua Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Edinson Cavani\" title=\"tien dao Edinson Cavani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/ac-milan-muon-trao-doi-cau-thu-voi-psg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">PSG mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Karim Benzema thay Cavani<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t m\u0169i c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi thay Cavani, ngo\u00e0i ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed c\u1ee7a Neymar, PSG c\u0169ng nh\u1eafm Robert Lewandowski, Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Karim Benzema. Nh\u01b0ng so v\u1edbi 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Real c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u1ea3 thi h\u01a1n c\u1ea3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nBenzema kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Real v\u00e0 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ed3i. Anh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/benzema-roi-real-sang-trung-quoc-180-183623.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Benzema t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c</strong></span> b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 PSG mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Karim Benzema.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng PSG tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-dai-dien-chinh-thuc-chot-tuong-lai-neymar-184-184146.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-psg-tranh-gianh-kenedy-172-184027.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 PSG tranh gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/tan-hlv-cua-psg-muon-rut-ruot-chelsea-197-184021.html\">T\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a PSG mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-psg-danh-tieng-voi-nhung-doi-bong-o-premier-league-172-183931.html\">Sao PSG \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-gui-psg-pogba-martial-neymar-172-183797.html\">MU g\u1eedi PSG: Pogba + Martial = Neymar?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1124","checkdouble":"184153"},{"date":"10:32 13/04","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khuy\u00ean Chelsea gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Conte v\u00e0 b\u00e1n 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/huyen-thoai