00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1edbi ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 sau k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, vi\u1ec7c Conte kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i trong chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huyen thoai khuyen Chelsea giu chan Conte va ban 5 cau thu hinh anh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khuy\u00ean Chelsea gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Conte v\u00e0 b\u00e1n 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/huyen-thoai-khuyen-chelsea-ban-cau-thu-thay-vi-sa-thai-conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Desailly khuy\u00ean Chelsea gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Chelsea?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sa-thai-conte-loi-giai-nua-voi-cho-bai-toan-tram-kha-172-179725.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen sa th\u1ea3i c\u00e1c HLV</span> khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Champions League. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Nh\u01b0ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Marcel Desailly tin r\u1eb1ng The Blues n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Conte v\u00e0 thanh l\u00fd m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Conte \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9t nhi\u00ean thi\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed5i HLV v\u00e0 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i HLV v\u00e0 thanh l\u00fd 4 ho\u1eb7c 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;, Desailly chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Daily Mail.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. \u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Chelsea c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd mong mu\u1ed1n. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0o.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang-172-183929.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang-172-183929.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n sa th\u1ea3i Conte nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span><br>\r\n<span>BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdp g\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai HLV Conte. Theo Daily Mail, Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i nh\u01b0 Moses hay Alonso \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat. Chelsea c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u00ecn chung, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Chelsea. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Conte. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i cho \u00f4ng \u1ea5y th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB&nbsp;Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ly-do-chelsea-ban-eden-hazard-172-184119.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/drinkwater-co-the-roi-chelsea-chi-sau-mot-mua-giai-172-184108.html\">Drinkwater c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dang-le-chelsea-nen-giu-lai-diego-costa-172-184060.html\">\u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd Chelsea n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Diego Costa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-psg-tranh-gianh-kenedy-172-184027.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 PSG tranh gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Chelsea<