k;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U quan t\u00e2m Ryan Sessegnon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ryan Sessegnon \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean hot nh\u1ea5t \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 17 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Ryan Sessegnon thay Luke Shaw o He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"MU mua Ryan Sessegnon thay Luke Shaw \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/5/mu-nhan-tin-buon-vu-sao-fulham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU quan t\u00e2m Sessegnon \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 2000 \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Fulham, anh r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n khi l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t cho ph\u00e9p Sessegnon th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u0103ng l\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t v\u00e0o trong.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 42 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Fulham \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 2000 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t. MU mua Sessegnon thay Luke Shaw c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6 n\u00e0y. Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/psg-bat-ngo-nhay-vao-tranh-sessegnon-voi-mu-184-177026.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG quan t\u00e2m Sessegnon</strong></span>.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nFulham l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 M.U v\u1ee5 Ryan Sessegnon</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Evening Standard, Fulham quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Craven Cottage \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Fulham cho r\u1eb1ng Sessegnon l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n anh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Ryan Sessegnon thay Luke Shaw o He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"MU mua Ryan Sessegnon thay Luke Shaw \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/22/Hau-ve-Ryan-Sessegnon-bi-HLV-Fulham-canh-bao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fulham quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Ryan Sessegnon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Sessegnon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Fulham v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 17 tu\u1ed5i, \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Fulham c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-mu-nhan-loi-canh-bao-172-176471.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Fulham c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o&nbsp;Sessegnon,</strong></span> \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u thay v\u00ec quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 Fulham ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 2000 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, song nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Theo Mirror, c\u1ea3 M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea ho\u1eb7c M.U b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Sessegnon s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao 17 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1122","checkdouble":"184148"},{"date":"11:24 13/04","title":"V\u00ec ti\u1ec1n, Courtois b\u1ecf Chelsea t\u1edbi PSG?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/22/vi-tien-courtois-bo-chelsea-toi-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size