ext-align: justify;\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda The Blues nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG dung tien dua Thibaut Courtois roi Chelsea o He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"PSG d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0a Thibaut Courtois r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/PSG-dung-tien-dua-Thibaut-Courtois-roi-Chelsea-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Courtois chia tay Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/courtois-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-172-182860.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Courtois l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</strong></span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ra \u0111i, anh \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ramos-va-ronaldo-muon-real-mua-thu-mon-cua-chelsea-180-181590.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Courtois</strong></span>, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Los Blancos c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Navas, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n, Chelsea, song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u1eef Courtois \u1edf l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. The Blues \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>PSG b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Thibaut Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo RMC Sport, PSG \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a Thibaut Courtois r\u1eddi Chelsea. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois nhan loi vi sai lam dan den ban mo ti so cua Messi.\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u00ec sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Messi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/courtois-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n Courtois chia tay Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, PSG ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, qua \u0111\u00f3 bi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlphonse Areola \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a PSG, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai, mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Courtois v\u00e0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Chelsea</strong></span> ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gia h\u1ea1n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Blues s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y anh kh\u1ecfi Stamford Bridge, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/70988-40942/033100\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1121","checkdouble":"184149"},{"date":"11:39 13/04","title":"Morata b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/9/morata-bao-chua-cho-mua-giai-te-hai-o-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepann