argin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd sau khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Morata kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n sau 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Morata \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng phanh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 1. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n qua 22 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u ph\u00eda.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nguyen nhan Morata thi dau that vong o Chelsea hinh anh\" title=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Morata thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/25/Nguyen-nhan-Morata-thi-dau-that-vong-o-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb1ng sau s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/an-the-do-khong-dang-morata-bi-conte-chi-trich-172-178104.html\" target=\"_blank\">Morata ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Norwich</span> t\u1ea1i FA Cup, anh \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t g\u1ea7n 1 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1edbi khi t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 magn ni\u1ec1m vui v\u1ec1 cho CLB c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Chelsea \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Morata kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh London. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh London l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean t\u1edd Gazzetta dello Sport.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o xanh.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-khuyen-chelsea-ban-cau-thu-thay-vi-sa-thai-conte-172-184147.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/huyen-thoai-khuyen-chelsea-ban-cau-thu-thay-vi-sa-thai-conte.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-khuyen-chelsea-ban-cau-thu-thay-vi-sa-thai-conte-172-184147.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khuy\u00ean Chelsea gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Conte v\u00e0 b\u00e1n 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\n<span>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Marcel Desailly cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea n\u00ean gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Conte. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 The Blues c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 thanh l\u00fd 4 hay 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i trong...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng hay n\u01a1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Davide Zappacosta lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0a t\u00f4i t\u1edbi s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-alvaro-morata-cua-chelsea-172-183915.html\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u201cbom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/morata-sap-tai-hop-james-rodriguez-172-183209.html\">Morata s\u1eafp t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p James Rodriguez?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/conte-so-harry-kane-nhung-vung-tin-vao-morata-172-183095.html\">Conte s\u1ee3 Harry Kane nh\u01b0ng v\u1eefng tin v\u00e0o Morata</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diego-costa-dong-cam-voi-nguoi-ke-nhiem-o-chelsea-172-182580.html\">Diego Costa \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/morata-nghi-gi-khi-bi-que-huong-bo-roi-172-182509.html\">Morata ngh\u0129 g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecf r\u01a1i?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pedro-ca-ngoi-su-tro-lai-cua-morata-172-182507.html\">Pedro ca ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Morata</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong