th\u00eam n\u1eefa.&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League 2017-18, Atletico Madrid thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sporting CP. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha thua v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u khi Sporting CP c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Fredy Montero.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antoine Griezmann bo lo co hoi ghi ban trong tran thua Sporting CP.\" title=\"Antoine Griezmann b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn thua Sporting CP.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/atletico-madrid-khong-the-doi-hoi-nhieu-hon-tu-antoine-griezmann.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Antoine Griezmann b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn thua Sporting CP.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng Atletico v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/bon-doi-lot-vao-ban-ket-europa-league-ky-tich-tu-ga-nhuoc-tieu-184-184131.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</span></span> v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn thua Sporting CP, Antoine Griezmann c\u00f3 hai c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Atletico tho\u00e1t thua nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1ch Antoine Griezmann</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Diego Simeone l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &quot;Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb Griezmann v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho Atletico. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong \u0111\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u1ea3. Sporting CP l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ebd ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi hai b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, Atletico v\u1eabn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c HLV Simeone b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Griezmann l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd b\u1edfi trong 16 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 17 b\u00e0n. T\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Atletico l\u00e0 Arsenal, Marseille ho\u1eb7c hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Salzburg.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-muon-tay-pogba-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-nay-trong-he-toi-172-183972.html\">Mourinho m\u01b0\u1ee3n tay Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y trong h\u00e8 t\u1edbi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-atletico-180-183874.html\">Real Madrid chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Atletico</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dam-phan-voi-barca-180-183819.html\">Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Barca?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/umtiti-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-griezmann-180-183457.html\">Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Griezmann?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xuat-hien-rao-can-cho-chuyen-nhuong-barca-mua-griezmann-180-182919.html\">Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n cho Barca trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Griezmann</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-muon-barca-mua-sao-liverpool-thay-vi-griezmann-180-182889.html\">Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua sao Liverpool thay v\u00ec Griezmann</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1119","checkdouble":"184137"},{"date":"09:12 13/04","title":"Wenger ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Mkhitaryan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/22/wenger-tiet-lo-qua-trinh-hoi-phuc-chan-thuo