"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mkhitaryan chan thuong kha nghiem trong\" title=\"Mkhitaryan ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/arsenal-nhan-tin-soc-tu-chan-thuong-cua-mkhitaryan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mkhitaryan ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nhan-tin-soc-tu-chan-thuong-cua-mkhitaryan-172-183888.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Mkhitaryan ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a </strong></span>\u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ebfn, n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. NHM Arsenal \u0111ang r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u sao M.U g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, HLV Wenger \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00f9a. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Mkhitaryan \u0111ang b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau hai tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Arsenal, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n Mkhitaryan trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Wenger h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 v\u1edbi CSKA Moscow r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay gi\u00fap Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-3 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Arsene Wenger thua nhan Arsenal da mang tam ly chu quan.\" title=\"HLV Arsene Wenger th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u1ee7 quan.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/hoa-hu-via-cska-moscow-hlv-arsene-wenger-thua-nhan-arsenal-qua-chu-quan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Arsene Wenger h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng sau t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nHLV Wenger t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng m\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh cho Welbeck nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1118","checkdouble":"184140"},{"date":"07:19 13/04","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 17h00 ng\u00e0y 13/4 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/Truoc-vong-5-V-League-2018-Vong-dau-cua-cac-doi-khach-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:le